description: Try our easy to follow Teriyaki beef & veggie bowls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Teriyaki beef & veggie bowls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 450 g Woolworths COOK stir fry hokkien noodles
500 g Heart Smart beef stir fry
250 g superfood vegetable stir fry mix

recipeInstructions.text: Add noodles and teriyaki sauce to wok. Stir-fry for 2 minutes or until well coated and heated through. Return beef to wok. Toss to combine. Serve.
